   - Vercel shadow-as-border for table rows
   - Pill badges (9999px radius) for difficulty/tags

3. **Forms**: Button, Input, Select, TextArea, Form
   - Refs: `frontend/src/components/ui/Button.tsx`, `frontend/src/components/ui/Input.tsx`
   - Linear-style ghost/primary/destructive variants
